Episode 1 - Chapter 1
=====================

The protagonist (Unlikely Fighter) juggles his unfulfilling career corporate office life into an illegal fights ring for heavily modified individuals. The episode ends with the dissaperance of the Unlikely Fighter after his shot for a big title. 


The Unlikely Fighter fights his first 3 fights in his hometown of the Basque Urban Coast. 

Intro
-----

- Intro to the game and "this were my choices" list
	- Govtube as mean to tell story - Today EU congress illegalized all current and past body modifications. If you have one, please submit to health authorities...
	- Regret of fighter as personality choice
	- Choice of past decisions
	- Background
- First day of work




Main endings
------------

After achieving enough notoriety (through both winning fights and publicity stunts), he gets an offer to join an international fighting circuit. There are 2 variations to this ending:

- Keeps his job 
- Quits his job


Minor good endings
------------------

- The fighter manages to go up the corporate ladder enough to be comfortable, only has minor mods, and hasn't been revealed as an illegal cyborg.
- The fighter is revealed as an illegal cyborg and loses his job, but manages to escape police.

Minor bad endings
-----------------

- The fighter dies because of health complications after too many bad fights and surgeries.
- The fighter loses his mind to mind mods and/or corporate nootropics.
- The fighter gets arrested for illegal mods. 